ROBOGATCHI

little electronic pet

Metrics:
HEALTH
HAPPYNESS

Status':
HUNGRY
SATIATED
FULL
TIRED
ENERGETIC
PLAYFUL
ANGRY
LOVING
TALKATIVE
LONELY

Stages:
EGG
BABY
CHILD
TEEN
ADULT

Interactions:
PET
WALK
PLAY
LISTEN
HUG
FEED


Robogatchi's are individual
Each one will have a name, images which correlate to Stages
 and visual changes which correlate to Status
Individuals will have different attitudes and respond differently
 to stimuli

